Defect Detail Panel

Clicking any defect opens a detail panel showing the complete failure
report (Layer 2, Section 6.2 format) plus resolution history. For test
failures, this includes the exact inputs, expected value with oracle
citation, actual value, and variance. For data quality findings, this
includes the affected member(s), the evidence, and the proposed
correction. Every defect links to its Change Impact Assessment if one
exists, and to the relevant rule in the business rules inventory.

3.3 Trends View (Strategic)

The Trends View serves supervisors, QA leadership, and executives. It
answers: "Is system quality improving or degrading over time? Are our
prevention practices working?"

